%N A396277 Triangle T(n,k), n >= 0, 0 <= k <= (4^n-1)/3, read by rows, where T(n,k) = [x^k] (F_n(x)/x)^(1/3) and F_n(x) is the n-th iteration of x*(1 + x)^3.
%H A396277 Seiichi Manyama, <a href="/A396277/b396277.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..7286</a> (rows 0..7)
%F A396277 (F_n(x)/x)^(1/3) = Product_{j=0..n-1} (1 + F_j(x)).
%F A396277 T(n,k) = Sum_{0 = x_0 <= x_1 <= ... <= x_{n-1} <= x_n = k} Product_{j=0..n-1} binomial(3*x_j + 1,x_{j+1} - x_j).
%e A396277 F_0(x) = x.
%e A396277 F_1(x) = x + 3*x^2 + 3*x^3 + x^4.
%e A396277 F_2(x) = x + 6*x^2 + 24*x^3 + 74*x^4 + 180*x^5 + 363*x^6 + 616*x^7 + 876*x^8 + 1044*x^9 + 1032*x^10 + 819*x^11 + 498*x^12 + 220*x^13 + 66*x^14 + 12*x^15 + x^16.
%e A396277 F_3(x) = x + 9*x^2 + 63*x^3 + 381*x^4 + 2052*x^5 + 10053*x^6 + 45390*x^7 + ... + x^64.
